GingerCore.Actions.ActDBValidation.Description: Fetch Available MDN State and City
GingerCore.Actions.ActDBValidation.SQL: with r as (select /*+ index_ffs(r,RM1_RESOURCE_1IX) parallel_index(r,RM1_RESOURCE_1IX,8) materialize */ distinct substr(r.resource_value,1,3) np, substr(r.resource_value,4,3) nx,resource_value from rm1_resource r where r.resource_status='AVAILABLE' and r.resource_type_id=1 and r.resource_pool_id = 1 )select CITY,STATE from (select g.geo_city as CITY, l.state as STATE, count(distinct r.resource_value) as MDNS from urm1_lerg l, r, URM9_GEO_LERG_CITY_MAP g where l.npa=r.np and l.nxx=r.nx and g.state=l.state and g.lerg_city=l.city group by g.geo_city,l.state ) where MDNS > 20 order by MDNS desc

GingerCore.Actions.ActInputValue.Value: with r as (select /*+ index_ffs(r,RM1_RESOURCE_1IX) parallel_index(r,RM1_RESOURCE_1IX,8) materialize */ distinct substr(r.resource_value,1,3) np, substr(r.resource_value,4,3) nx,resource_value from rm1_resource r where r.resource_status='AVAILABLE' and r.resource_type_id=1 and r.resource_pool_id = 1 )select CITY,STATE from (select g.geo_city as CITY, l.state as STATE, count(distinct r.resource_value) as MDNS from urm1_lerg l, r, URM9_GEO_LERG_CITY_MAP g where l.npa=r.np and l.nxx=r.nx and g.state=l.state and g.lerg_city=l.city group by g.geo_city,l.state ) where MDNS > 20 order by MDNS desc
